BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (1-13 and is when your baby transforms from a tiny cluster of cells into a fully) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 623 Td (formed miniature human with all major organs in place.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (Common first trimester symptoms include morning sickness \(which can happen at) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (any time of day\), extreme fatigue, frequent urination, tender breasts, food) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (aversions or cravings, and heightened sense of smell. Not every woman) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 553 Td (experiences all of these, and severity varies greatly.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Your first prenatal appointment usually happens around weeks 8-10. Your provider) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (will confirm the pregnancy, estimate your due date, order blood work, and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 498 Td (discuss your medical history. This is a great time to ask all your questions -) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 483 Td (no question is too small or silly.) Tj ET
