BT 0.1 g /F2 15 Tf 259.2 720 Td (PRENATAL CARE) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 253.2 695 Td (Throughout Pregnancy) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (Prenatal care is your roadmap to a healthy pregnancy. Regular appointments allow) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (your provider to catch potential issues early, monitor baby's growth, and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (support your physical and emotional health throughout this journey.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (Schedule of typical visits: monthly in the first and second trimesters, biweekly) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (from weeks 28-36, and weekly from week 36 until delivery. Each visit includes) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (weight check, blood pressure, urine test, fundal height measurement, and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (listening to baby's heartbeat.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (Important prenatal tests: first trimester screening \(weeks 11-14\), anatomy scan) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (ultrasound \(weeks 18-22\), glucose tolerance test \(weeks 24-28\), Group B Strep) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (test \(weeks 36-37\). Discuss which genetic tests you want with your provider.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 488 Td (Choosing your provider: OB/GYN \(physician specializing in pregnancy\), midwife) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (\(lower-intervention approach\), or family doctor. Consider their philosophy on) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (birth, hospital affiliation, and whether you feel heard and respected.) Tj ET

endstream
