BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 284.4 740 Td (Chapter 3) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 15 Tf 212.4 720 Td (NUTRITION DURING PREGNANCY) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 242.64 695 Td (Eating for Two \(Sort Of\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (You actually only need about 300 extra calories per day during pregnancy - that) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (is roughly an extra sandwich. Quality matters more than quantity. Your baby is) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (building bones, brain, muscles, and organs from the nutrients you provide.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (Essential nutrients: folic acid \(prevents neural tube defects - leafy greens,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (fortified cereals\), iron \(blood volume doubles - red meat, spinach, beans\),) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (calcium \(baby's bones - dairy, tofu, fortified OJ\), DHA \(brain development -) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (fatty fish, walnuts, supplements\), protein \(growth - meat, eggs, legumes\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (Foods to avoid: raw fish/sushi, unpasteurized cheeses, deli meats \(unless) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (heated\), high-mercury fish \(shark, swordfish\), raw eggs, unwashed produce,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (alcohol \(no safe amount during pregnancy\), and limit caffeine to 200mg daily) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 498 Td (\(about one 12-oz coffee\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (Morning sickness management: eat small meals frequently, keep crackers by your) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (bedside, try ginger \(tea, candies, supplements\), avoid triggers \(strong smells,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 443 Td (fatty foods\), stay hydrated with small sips, and talk to your doctor if you) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 428 Td (cannot keep food down.) Tj ET

endstream
