q 0.92 g 50 710 512 50 re f Q
BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 284.4 740 Td (Chapter 4) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 15 Tf 252.0 720 Td (EXERCISE SAFELY) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 210.96 695 Td (Staying Active While Growing a Human) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (Exercise during pregnancy is not just safe - it is recommended. Regular activity) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (reduces pregnancy complications, eases labor, improves mood, helps you sleep) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (better, and speeds postpartum recovery. The general rule: if you were doing it) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 623 Td (before pregnancy, you can likely continue with modifications.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (Safe exercises: walking, swimming, prenatal yoga, stationary cycling, light) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (weight training, low-impact aerobics. These provide cardiovascular benefits) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (without excessive joint stress or fall risk.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (Exercises to avoid: contact sports, activities with fall risk \(skiing, horseback) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (riding\), hot yoga or hot tubs, lying flat on your back after first trimester,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (heavy lifting that causes straining, and any exercise that causes pain,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 498 Td (dizziness, or bleeding.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (Listen to your body. Pregnancy is not the time to set personal records. Use the) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (talk test - you should be able to hold a conversation while exercising. Stay) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 443 Td (hydrated, avoid overheating, and stop immediately if you feel dizzy, have chest) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 428 Td (pain, or experience contractions.) Tj ET

endstream
