BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (The nesting instinct is real - many women feel a powerful urge to organize and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (prepare their home in the third trimester. Channel this energy wisely by) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (focusing on what actually matters rather than having a picture-perfect nursery.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (What baby actually needs: a safe sleep space \(crib, bassinet, or pack-n-play) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (with firm flat mattress\), car seat \(installed correctly before birth\), diapers) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (and wipes, basic clothing \(onesies, sleep sacks, hats\), feeding supplies, and a) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (few burp cloths.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (What can wait: a decorated nursery, a changing table \(any flat surface works\),) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (excessive clothes in multiple sizes, every baby gadget advertised. Babies need) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (very little in the first weeks - mostly you, food, warmth, and clean diapers.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 488 Td (Practical prep: cook and freeze meals, stock up on household essentials, prepare) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (pet introduction plan, set up a diaper station on each floor, pack hospital bag) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (by week 36, and arrange postpartum help.) Tj ET

