BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (For labor: comfortable robe or gown, grip socks, hair ties, lip balm, phone) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (charger \(long cord\), music playlist, focal point for breathing, light snacks for) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (early labor, and your birth plan \(if you have one\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 558 Td (For after delivery: comfortable going-home outfit \(think 6-months-pregnant) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (size\), nursing bra, nipple cream, thick pads \(hospital provides some\),) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (toiletries, flip flops for shower, pillow from home, and your own towel.) Tj ET
