BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 553 Td (breastfeeding initiation, eye ointment and vitamin K preferences.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Pain management options: unmedicated \(breathing, positions, water, massage\),) Tj ET
