BT 0.1 g /F2 15 Tf 241.2 720 Td (LABOR AND DELIVERY) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 276.96 695 Td (The Big Day) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (Labor has three stages. Stage 1: cervix dilates from 0-10cm \(longest stage, can) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (last hours to days\). Stage 2: pushing baby out \(minutes to hours\). Stage 3:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (delivering the placenta \(5-30 minutes\). Each woman's experience is unique.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (Early labor \(0-6cm\): contractions start and gradually intensify. You can usually) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (stay home during this phase. Time contractions. Go to hospital when they are 4-5) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (minutes apart, lasting 1 minute, for 1 hour \(the 4-1-1 rule\). Walk, rest, eat) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (lightly, and stay hydrated.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (Active labor and transition \(6-10cm\): contractions become intense and close) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (together. This is typically when you are at the hospital. Transition \(8-10cm\) is) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (the most intense part but also the shortest. You might feel pressure, nausea, or) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 498 Td (like you cannot do it. You CAN.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (Pushing and delivery: once fully dilated, you will feel an urge to push. Follow) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (your body's cues and your provider's guidance. Pushing can take minutes or) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 443 Td (hours, especially for first babies. Then suddenly - your baby is here and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 428 Td (everything changes forever.) Tj ET

endstream
