BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 250.56 695 Td (Feeding Your New Baby) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (Breastfeeding is natural but not always easy. It is a learned skill for both you) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (and baby. Most challenges resolve within the first few weeks with proper) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (support. Whether you breastfeed exclusively, supplement, or formula feed, your) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 623 Td (baby will thrive.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (Getting started: baby should nurse within the first hour after birth. Frequent) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (nursing in the first days establishes supply. Newborns nurse 8-12 times per day) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (\(every 2-3 hours\). Colostrum \(first milk\) is small in volume but packed with) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 553 Td (antibodies.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Common challenges: latching difficulties \(see a lactation consultant\), nipple) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (pain \(often from shallow latch\), engorgement \(warm compresses and frequent) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 498 Td (nursing\), low supply concerns \(usually perceived rather than actual - watch wet) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 483 Td (diapers, not clock\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (Support resources: hospital lactation consultants \(free during your stay\), La) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 443 Td (Leche League groups, local lactation consultants for home visits, breastfeeding) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 428 Td (hotlines, and online communities. Getting help early prevents most problems from) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 413 Td (escalating.) Tj ET

endstream
