BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 282.0 740 Td (Chapter 12) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 15 Tf 237.60000000000002 720 Td (POSTPARTUM RECOVERY) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 253.2 695 Td (The Fourth Trimester) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (Nobody talks enough about postpartum recovery. Your body just grew a human and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (birthed it - recovery takes TIME. The first six weeks are called the fourth) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (trimester for a reason. Be patient and kind with yourself.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (Physical recovery: bleeding \(lochia\) lasts 4-6 weeks, perineal soreness, uterus) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (contracting back to size \(afterpains, especially during nursing\), breast) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (engorgement, night sweats as hormones adjust, hair loss around 3-4 months, and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (general exhaustion.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (Emotional recovery: baby blues \(mood swings, crying, anxiety\) are normal for the) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (first 2 weeks. If feelings of sadness, anxiety, or disconnection persist beyond) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (2 weeks or intensify, this may be postpartum depression or anxiety - TELL YOUR) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 498 Td (PROVIDER. It is common \(1 in 7 women\) and treatable.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (Recovery tips: sleep when baby sleeps \(yes, really\), accept all help offered,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (keep snacks and water everywhere, do not compare your recovery to others, skip) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 443 Td (visitors if you need to, and remember that recovery is not linear.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
