q 0.92 g 50 710 512 50 re f Q
BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 282.0 740 Td (Chapter 13) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 15 Tf 223.2 720 Td (NEWBORN CARE FIRST WEEK) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 247.92000000000002 695 Td (Surviving and Thriving) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (The first week home with a newborn is overwhelming, beautiful, terrifying, and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (amazing all at once. Lower all expectations except keeping baby fed, dry, warm,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (and loved. Everything else can wait.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (Feeding: baby eats every 2-3 hours around the clock. Watch for hunger cues:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (rooting, lip smacking, hands to mouth. Do not wait for crying \(that is late) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (hunger\). Track wet and dirty diapers to ensure adequate intake \(aim for 6+ wet) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (diapers by day 5\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (Sleep: newborns sleep 16-17 hours but in short bursts of 2-4 hours. Always place) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (baby on back in a bare crib/bassinet \(no blankets, pillows, or stuffed animals\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (Room-sharing is recommended for the first 6 months but bed-sharing is not safe.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 488 Td (When to call the doctor: fever over 100.4F, not eating for 6+ hours, fewer than) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (3-4 wet diapers per day by day 4, yellow skin that worsens \(jaundice\),) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (inconsolable crying, or anything that feels wrong to you. Trust your instincts.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
