BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 282.0 740 Td (Chapter 14) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 15 Tf 205.2 720 Td (BUILDING YOUR SUPPORT SYSTEM) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 258.48 695 Td (It Takes a Village) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (You cannot do this alone, and you should not have to. Building your support) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (system before baby arrives ensures help is ready when you need it most. Identify) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (who can help with what and coordinate in advance.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (Types of support you need: practical \(meals, laundry, errands, cleaning\),) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (emotional \(listening without judgment, reassurance, validation\), informational) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (\(experienced moms, lactation consultants, pediatrician\), and physical \(someone) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (to hold baby while you shower or nap\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (How to ask for help: be specific \(instead of 'can you help?' try 'can you bring) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (dinner Tuesday?'\), create a meal train \(friends sign up for days\), accept every) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (offer, and let go of how things are done \(if someone folds laundry wrong, at) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 498 Td (least it is folded\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (Professional support: doula \(labor and postpartum support\), lactation) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (consultant, postpartum therapist, mommy groups, online communities. Investing in) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 443 Td (professional support is not a luxury - it is healthcare.) Tj ET

endstream
