BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 282.0 740 Td (Chapter 15) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 15 Tf 165.6 720 Td (THE EMOTIONAL JOURNEY OF BECOMING A MOM) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 11 Tf 276.96 695 Td (Matrescence) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 668 Td (Becoming a mother is not just a physical transformation. It is a complete) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 653 Td (identity shift called matrescence - as significant as adolescence. You are not) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 638 Td (just having a baby. You are becoming a new version of yourself.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (What is normal: grieving your old life while loving your new one, feeling) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (simultaneously overwhelmed with love and overwhelmed with responsibility, not) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 583 Td (feeling an instant bond \(it can take time\), wanting alone time and feeling) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 568 Td (guilty about it.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 543 Td (Your relationship will change. You and your partner are now parents, and that) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (transition is hard. Communication becomes essential. Schedule time to talk about) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 513 Td (feelings, divide responsibilities fairly, and remember you are on the same team.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 488 Td (The most important thing: you are already a good mother because you care enough) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 473 Td (to read this book, plan, and worry. Trust yourself. Your instincts are powerful.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 458 Td (And ask for help when you need it - that is strength, not weakness.) Tj ET

endstream
